off the shelf, and mission partner capabilities to continuously develop and field new and improved operational capabilities hosted on its open, hybrid cloud environment
to meet mission requirements. Contracting strategy involves a combination of Basic Ordering Agreements (BOAs), Indefinite Delivery/Indefinite Quantity (IDIQ)
contracts awarded to execute program funds and delivery/task orders are negotiated/awarded individually.

