A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
This project funds applied research; technology assessment, road mapping, and concept development; and less technologically mature projects within the Future Naval
Capability (FNC) process as means to inform, enhance, enable, and invent future concepts and capabilities with new Science and Technology (S&T). This project is
organized into ten activities, the core of which is represented by the eight Expeditionary Warfighting Capability Areas.

