in this PE can be classified between TRL 2 (technology concept and/or application formulation) and TRL 4 (component and/or breadboard validation in laboratory
environments).

 TCs are at lower Technology Readiness Level (TRLs) and focus on maturing technologies to higher TRLs to reduce FNC transition risk. The FNC Program favors a high
