-Continue development of a learning and planning framework, conducting field experiments that demonstrate
simultaneous exploration and navigation in an unknown environment while attempting to execute a complex
mission. The objective is to improve autonomous search capabilities for unmanned systems.

-Continue development of cooperative autonomous underwater vehicle behaviors that adapt to dynamic and
