operations at standoff distances.

-Continue Unmanned Systems Situational Awareness development of onboard processing in unmanned
systems to enable environmental situational awareness (SA) in the littorals.

-Continue Rapid Operational Clearance efforts to develop technologies to rapidly clear operational areas of
munitions. The objective is to decrease the amount of time needed for services to clear munitions and conduct
clearance operations at standoff.
