Title: Torpedo Hardkill Development                                                                                    0.000       0.000       8.143      0.000       8.143
                                                                                                       Articles:          -           -           -          -           -
Description: The NIXIE Hardkill (HK) System is an all-encompassing threat torpedo countermeasure system
that provides a torpedo hard kill capability to the Surface Navy. The System includes all the capabilities of
the AN/SLQ-25 NIXIE 25E System, the Torpedo Warning System (TWS), torpedo alertment and fire control
Capability, and includes the capability to launch a Compact Rapid Attack Weapon (CRAW) as the weapon

