D. Acquisition Strategy
The AoA was completed in 1QFY2023 and identified the need for an improved FVL (MS) Family of Systems (FoS) to respond to the future threat environment, resulting
in a recommendation for pre-Milestone A efforts and a Milestone A entry. Limited pre-Milestone A efforts began in FY 2024.

The Navy's Gate 2 Review was completed in 2QFY2025. The Gate 2 Decision identified the preferred alternatives of an Optionally Crewed Single Main Rotor Helicopter
or maximally common Crewed and Uncrewed Single Main Rotor Helicopters. The preferred alternative is to leverage a common avionics and mission systems

