(NSM) is a Force Design priority central to the Marine Corps' contribution to the Naval Expeditionary Force's (NEF) surface warfare campaign. The NSM includes the
missile, booster, shipping/launch container, flight software and associated items. The goal is to double the range of the current NSM missiles over the next five years.
